{"tid":2184030,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"剛入獄的手足: 總算能跟其他年輕抗爭手足同行","createTime":"2020-09-01T09:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T16:00:00.000Z","uid":134071,"like":87,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"103f440a104fe057dcba604c7a6a7259e5ae453e","tid":2184030,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:43:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/leo.tang.79656/posts/10157991037733853\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fleo.tang.79656%2Fposts%2F10157991037733853&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=8d4225e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/leo.tang.79656/posts/10157991037733853</a><br />\n<br />\nLeo Tang<br />\n1 小時  &middot;<br />\n<br />\n現在的牢獄，是用來困好人的。香港如是，加泰如是，現在白羅斯如是，泰國如是。<br />\n抗爭有時，入冊有時。一旦認識到自己與政權之間的關係，一旦覺得要「回應」，人就不得不反抗。<br />\n比起好多同輩友儕，我在2020年入獄，可以說是「遲」了。<strong>比起好多運動中相識的年輕手足，總算是與他們同行。</strong><br />\n<strong>我比好多人幸運</strong>。比我年輕的手足，一個個先被還押，等待一個更長的刑期；無名的抗爭者，流亡海外，未有歸期。在戰場上逝去的手足，催促我們繼續前行。所謂的沒有退路，並不是口號。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>這是煲底之約的必經之路</strong>，我們或許正為當下要做什麼事而躊躇，但對於這些「必經」，我們不必憂惱。<br />\n在街頭，我們與手足相遇；在世界，我們正置於各地的反抗浪潮。<strong>我們絕不孤單。</strong>"},{"pid":"0837ef78e81f00b2397525f7eac7987dd1471651","tid":2184030,"uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:44:07.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AA%8D%E8%97%8F%E4%BC%B8%E7%B8%AE%E6%A3%8D%E5%9B%9A-4-%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E8%81%B7%E5%B7%A5%E7%9B%9F%E5%B9%B9%E4%BA%8B%E9%84%A7%E5%BB%BA%E8%8F%AF-%E5%85%A5%E7%8D%84%E6%98%AF%E7%85%B2%E5%BA%95%E4%B9%8B%E7%B4%84%E5%BF%85%E7%B6%93%E4%B9%8B%E8%B7%AF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%2597%258F%25E4%25BC%25B8%25E7%25B8%25AE%25E6%25A3%258D%25E5%259B%259A-4-%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588-%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%25B7%25A